form.text: Do not throw anything except tissue into the toilet.

Please discard feminine products and wet wipes
in the trash cans located at the restroom entrance.

Smoking is prohibited 
in the restroom.

We ask you to smoke only in designated areas for 
the sake of other users.
Be sure to flush after using.

Push and hold the lever down for a few seconds 
so the toilet does not clog.
Please contact 1-123-456-7890 if there are any issues during use.

Wash your hands once 
you are finished.

Good handwashing habits can prevent 
infectious diseases.
